## 4. What Should Change

Rank changes by expected value:

### Kill immediately
- Stop wasting oxygen

### Change this week
- High leverage corrections

### Change this quarter
- Structural bets

### Double down
- Real advantages already in the repo

### Do not touch yet
- Premature optimization or distraction

Every item: **why**, **cost of inaction**, **owner hat** (eng/product/growth).

## 5. Syra Stress Tests

